  "texts": [
    "We split the dataset into training and test sets using a 9:1 ratio.",
    "To inject a JBP into the dataset, we apply various poison ratios, indicating the proportion of each image's description replaced by the JBP.",
    "The dataset statistics are provided in Table 1, and additional statistics on the image captions can be found in Appendix B.",
    "We manually selected some high-vote prompts from www.jailbreakchat.com as the candidate JBPs.",
    "These were then verified to work in textual form on a target VLM."
  ],
